item.title: September 2020 - update
item.description: It’s been quite a long time since my last update. Things that I’ve done since May - I completed a short course at City, University of London - Introduction to Data Analytics and Machine Learning with Python Attended an online webinar hosted by IBM on quantum computing - Throwing the dice with a Quantum Computer Set up another Ethereum 2.
